# ENTITY::GET_ENTITY_UPRIGHT_VALUE

## Parameters
* **ENTITY_INDEX** entity

## Returns
* **FLOAT**

## Description
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Gets an up right value  between 1.0 being upright and -1.0 being upside down
